author: AP
title: IOC declines to blame Olympic boxing event for virus cases
description: IOC declines to blame Olympic boxing event for virus cases
content:
LAUSANNE, Switzerland (AP) — The IOC said Thursday it is “not aware of any link” between an Olympic boxing tournament it oversaw in London this month and positive coronavirus tests for people who were there.
